                    <p>You may terminate our services at any time by:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Providing written notice to our office (email acceptable)</li>
                        <li>Requesting withdrawal of pending applications</li>
                        <li>Ceasing to engage our ongoing services</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Termination does not affect obligations for completed services or fees already incurred.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Termination by EVFBS</h3>
                    <p>We may terminate services immediately if:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>You breach these Terms and fail to remedy within 7 days of notice</li>
                        <li>You provide false or misleading information materially affecting the service</li>
                        <li>Payment of fees is overdue by more than 14 days</li>
                        <li>Your conduct becomes unprofessional or damages our reputation</li>
                        <li>We determine that continuing services would breach our regulatory obligations</li>
                        <li>Your business becomes ineligible for our services (e.g., enters administration)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Effect of Termination</h3>
                    <p>Upon termination:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Immediate Effect:</strong> No further services will be provided from the termination date</li>
                        <li><strong>Outstanding Fees:</strong> All accrued fees and expenses become immediately payable</li>
                        <li><strong>Pending Applications:</strong> We will notify lenders of withdrawal unless instructed otherwise</li>
                        <li><strong>Documentation:</strong> We will provide copies of relevant documents and correspondence</li>
                        <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> Mutual confidentiality obligations continue indefinitely</li>
                        <li><strong>Commission Rights:</strong> We retain rights to commission for completed introductions</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Post-Termination Obligations</h3>
                    <p>Following termination, you agree to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Complete payment of all outstanding fees and expenses</li>
                        <li>Return any confidential materials or intellectual property</li>
                        <li>Refrain from disparaging our reputation or services</li>
                        <li>Honour any ongoing lender relationships established through our introduction</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Survival of Terms</h3>
                    <p>The following provisions survive termination:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Fee payment obligations and commission entitlements</li>
                        <li>Confidentiality and intellectual property protections</li>
                        <li>Limitation of liability and indemnity provisions</li>
                        <li>Dispute resolution and governing law clauses</li>
                        <li>Data protection and privacy obligations</li>
                    </ul>

                    <div class="highlight-box">
