                        <p>
                            Termination of services does not affect our entitlement to:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Upfront commission for loans settled through our introduction</li>
                            <li>Trail commission for existing loans during their term</li>
                            <li>Professional service fees for completed work</li>
