                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Dispute Resolution Process</h3>
                    <p>
                        We are committed to resolving disputes fairly and efficiently through our established complaints process.
                    </p>

                    <div class="process-steps">
                        <div class="step">
                            <div class="step-number">1</div>
                            <div class="step-content">
