                                <p>Direct discussion with your service consultant or account manager to identify and resolve concerns promptly:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Immediate discussion of service concerns</li>
                                    <li>Good faith negotiation and problem-solving</li>
                                    <li>Escalation to senior management if required</li>
