                                <h4>Formal Complaints Process</h4>
                                <p>Written complaint to our Complaints Officer if internal resolution is unsuccessful:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Submit complaint in writing with supporting documentation</li>
                                    <li>Acknowledgment within 7 days with reference number</li>
                                    <li>Investigation and response within 30 days</li>
                                    <li>Independent review and resolution recommendations</li>
                                </ul>
