                                <ul>
                                    <li>Free external dispute resolution service</li>
                                    <li>Binding decisions on financial service disputes</li>
                                    <li>Professional and impartial review process</li>
                                    <li>Alternative to court proceedings</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

