                        <li><strong>Expert Determination:</strong> Industry expert assessment for technical finance disputes</li>
                        <li><strong>Arbitration:</strong> Binding arbitration under Queensland Commercial Arbitration Act 2013</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>Legal Proceedings</h3>
                    <p>
                        Court proceedings may only be commenced after exhausting dispute resolution processes, except for:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Urgent injunctive relief or asset protection</li>
                        <li>Debt recovery for undisputed amounts</li>
                        <li>Intellectual property infringement claims</li>
                        <li>Regulatory compliance enforcement</li>
                    </ul>

