                            <li>Fair and reasonable settlement offers where appropriate</li>
                            <li>Compliance with external determination decisions</li>
                            <li>Process improvements based on complaint feedback</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            Our goal is professional resolution that maintains ongoing business relationships where possible.
                        </p>
